long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like bouncing balls! Show your skill in the game of bouncing the ball with the head. Soccer Header is a fun bouncing game that combines the excitement and skill of football with a 2D pixel design. There are three different footballer characters in the game; you can enjoy the game by choosing the one you want among these characters.

The aim of the game is quite simple: to get the highest score possible! However, achieving this is not so easy. The pixel design of the game gives you a nostalgic feeling and reflects your passion for football in a fun way.

Each character has their unique abilities and playstyle. When choosing your football player, you can create your strategy by considering these features. Every ball you bounce will get you one step closer to achieving higher scores.

Soccer Header is a game that players of all ages can enjoy with its immersive gameplay and simple controls. You can succeed using quick reflexes, kicks at the right time, and skillfully using the goalposts.

Soccer Header is for you if you want to combine your love of football with your skills. Experience the magic of football with vintage pixel graphics, improve your bounce skills, and show up on the pitch for the highest score.

How To Play
Played with Arrow Keys.

Soccer Header Sports Game Features
✓ 3 Different Character
✓ Pixel Graphics
✓ Easy control

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Soccer Header Sports Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
